Package: SeuratVisPro
Type: Package
Title: Innovative Visualization and Analysis Toolkit for Seurat v5
Version: 0.1.0
URL: https://github.com/benben-miao/SeuratVisPro
BugReports: https://github.com/benben-miao/SeuratVisPro/issues
Authors@R: person(given = "Benben", family = "Miao", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "benben.miao@outlook.com")
Description: A collection of innovative functions that address common pain points in single-cell RNA-seq analysis and visualization using Seurat v5. Includes interactive QC, cluster stability assessment, marker atlas visualization, batch mixing diagnostics, gene trend plotting, ligand-receptor scoring, cluster dendrograms, spatial overlays, module score visualization, and cell cycle views. Ships with a Shiny app to explore key features.
Depends: R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    patchwork,
